class.doc:
This is a special case Expression and violates some of the rules of an Expression. Violation: It has multiple Uids ( though not tracked there can be multiple uids for this expression )
This is a special operator which handles the case described below Tuple( a:int, b:bag{ b_a:int, b_b:float } ) --> BagDereference ( 0 ) --> project( 0, 1 ) --> bag{ b_a:float }
i.e. First input ( 0 ), second column ( 1 ) and first column of the bag.

